### 1. 创建一个新菜品 (POST 请求)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "砂锅烩面",
  "description": "来一碗羊汤砂锅烩面暖暖身子",
  "price": 10.00,
  "imageUrl": "http://example.com/images/gongbao.jpg"
}

### 2. 查询所有菜品 (GET 请求，用于验证)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 3. 更新 ID 为 ? 的菜品 (PUT 请求)
# (我们将“煎扒鱼”的价格从 70 改为 88)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "煎扒鱼 (精品)",
  "description": "经典红烧，味道醇厚，已降价",
  "price": 70.0,
  "imageUrl": "http://example.com/images/gongbao.jpg",
  "available": true
}

### 4. 删除 ID 为 ? 的菜品 (DELETE 请求)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/3

### 5. (最终验证) 再次查询所有菜品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

